    "long_instructions": "#Style Your Webpage to Match Your Brand Identity\r\n\r\nYour goal is to apply your brand’s colors and fonts to create a consistent, professional look across the entire page.\r\n\r\n\r\n:::details [*Don't have your own brand kit? You can use one of the following:*]\r\n- [Brand Kit 1](https://drive.google.com/file/d/1zP5Qf3FTBcnnlwH0029n1oq86OuGTRjG/view?usp=drive_link)\r\n- [Brand Kit 2](https://drive.google.com/file/d/1cXAC7aI2MidOgGQpDN71p19ybpG4JXV8/view?usp=drive_link)\r\n:::\r\n\r\n:::details [Helpful Steps]\r\n1. Generate the Initial Style\r\n2. Refine the Design\r\n3. Preview Your Work\r\n4. Save as Version 1\r\n:::",
